flowchart TD
  START([execute policyId + fn + fallback?]) --> RESOLVE[resolve policy + checksum integrity]
  RESOLVE --> BULK{bulkhead slot?}
  BULK -->|full| BFB{fallback?}
  BFB -->|yes| FB[FallbackExecuted · return fallback]
  BFB -->|no| BERR[throw BulkheadFullError]
  BULK -->|slot| ACQ[active++ · ExecutionStarted]

  ACQ --> GATE{circuit canAttempt?}
  GATE -->|open → half_open| HALF[save state · CircuitHalfOpened]
  HALF --> ATTEMPT
  GATE -->|open, window not elapsed| CFB{fallback?}
  CFB -->|yes| FB
  CFB -->|no| CERR[throw CircuitOpenError]
  GATE -->|closed / half_open| ATTEMPT[attempt loop 1..maxAttempts]

  ATTEMPT --> RUN[run fn with timeout]
  RUN --> OK{resolved in time?}
  OK -->|yes| SUCCESS[commit onSuccess\nhalf_open→closed → CircuitClosed + RecoveryCompleted\nExecutionSucceeded]
  OK -->|threw / timeout| CLS{classify retriable?}
  CLS -->|retriable & attempts left| RETRY[retryAttempts++ · backoff computed]
  RETRY --> ATTEMPT
  CLS -->|no more / non-retriable| FAIL[commit onFailure\nclosed→open at threshold → CircuitOpened\nExecutionFailed]

  FAIL --> FFB{fallback?}
  FFB -->|yes| FB
  FFB -->|no| THROW[throw lastError]

  SUCCESS --> DONE([active-- · result])
  FB --> DONE
  THROW --> DONE
  CERR --> DONE
  BERR --> DONE
